name: Smelly Foot Doctor Toe Nail Hospital
name_original: Smelly Foot Doctor Toe Nail Hospital
description:
5 Patients have come to the Foot Doctor all with the same problem, they all have stinky feet!

In this fantastic game for all ages you play the Foot Doctor, who has the job to clean these feet and get them back to a shiny fresh glow!

Use realistic tools such as;

Water hose to clean away mud!
Sponges to clean the bacteria monsters away!
Tweezers to pinch away objects!
Plasters to heal cuts!
& Much more!

This game gives you all the fun of being a foot doctor, without the smell!

Download it today, after all, nobody likes stinky feet!
